fields.description:
Report from the public: https://twitter.com/darthted/status/958901001146195969
{quote}
Excuse me @Atlassian but all the examples on how to configure the new issue view window fail to render in the docs - https://confluence.atlassian.com/jirasoftwarecloud/configuring-the-issue-detail-view-764478043.html
{quote}

h3. Problem Definition
Currently, when customer click expired invitation link, error display:-
{noformat}
sd.email.agent.invitation.invalid.token
{noformat}

h3. Suggested Solution
Provide a user friendly error in order customer to understand. For example:-
{noformat}
The invitation link is expired. If you already have an account, kindly use your user credential
{noformat}

h3. Why this is important
Better understanding for the customer.
